  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/4c356dce3cb4e10d1552844b1adfde65.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=55 /></span><br>Terra Toy is a simple and peaceful creative sandbox where you sculpt terrain and place down objects to create the scenic planet of your dreams. There is no goal or game; Build whatever you wish simply for the beauty of it using the easy-to-use tools and extensive library of decorations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/5fbba6afd833aa98b9366038f292e470.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/2dcdf4ec0d0b808f138f585e2e7adc52.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/2dcdf4ec0d0b808f138f585e2e7adc52.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/2dcdf4ec0d0b808f138f585e2e7adc52.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sculpt and terraform the terrain, raising it to erect hills and mountains, lowering it to reveal valleys and rivers, and smoothing it to achieve a photogenic finish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/587a7ab7d2c3de2ad9e59a476b3a978c.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/14cf702cfa79bb069fd3e780c35e5092.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/14cf702cfa79bb069fd3e780c35e5092.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/14cf702cfa79bb069fd3e780c35e5092.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Paint a colorful set of biomes onto the planet, creating varying environments and adding a sense of diversity and structure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/5c47e0ab64ff43743c1be0971f6e69c3.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/74c4e2db461ec253bb78a02f1d8c3fc9.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/74c4e2db461ec253bb78a02f1d8c3fc9.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/74c4e2db461ec253bb78a02f1d8c3fc9.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Place props to add detail and life to the world, choosing among many unique items to customize and plop onto the ground.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/0807fdd41cd1acac567a6953f33d42dc.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/7aa2f1336566cf3f22ea91d83cd48953.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/7aa2f1336566cf3f22ea91d83cd48953.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/7aa2f1336566cf3f22ea91d83cd48953.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take screenshots of your planet to share with your friends, or just simply sit around and watch the sun rise and the rain fall on your cozy little planet.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/4c356dce3cb4e10d1552844b1adfde65.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=55 /></span><br>Terra Toy is a simple and peaceful creative sandbox where you sculpt terrain and place down objects to create the scenic planet of your dreams. There is no goal or game; Build whatever you wish simply for the beauty of it using the easy-to-use tools and extensive library of decorations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/5fbba6afd833aa98b9366038f292e470.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/2dcdf4ec0d0b808f138f585e2e7adc52.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/2dcdf4ec0d0b808f138f585e2e7adc52.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/2dcdf4ec0d0b808f138f585e2e7adc52.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sculpt and terraform the terrain, raising it to erect hills and mountains, lowering it to reveal valleys and rivers, and smoothing it to achieve a photogenic finish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/587a7ab7d2c3de2ad9e59a476b3a978c.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/14cf702cfa79bb069fd3e780c35e5092.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/14cf702cfa79bb069fd3e780c35e5092.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/14cf702cfa79bb069fd3e780c35e5092.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Paint a colorful set of biomes onto the planet, creating varying environments and adding a sense of diversity and structure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/5c47e0ab64ff43743c1be0971f6e69c3.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/74c4e2db461ec253bb78a02f1d8c3fc9.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/74c4e2db461ec253bb78a02f1d8c3fc9.webm?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/74c4e2db461ec253bb78a02f1d8c3fc9.mp4?t=1698422416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Place props to add detail and life to the world, choosing among many unique items to customize and plop onto the ground.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/0807fdd41cd1acac567a6953f33d42dc.webp?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=45 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/7aa2f1336566cf3f22ea91d83cd48953.poster.avif?t=1698422416\" width=560 height=240 ><source src